{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"8748d033-b61e-496d-a1bb-52fbf52a3615","content":"Here's how to set up NuGet trusted publishing with OIDC from GitHub Actions:\n\n## Two steps required:\n\n### 1. Configure nuget.org\n\nOn [nuget.org](https://www.nuget.org) → Your account → **Manage Packages** → **Trusted Publishers**:\n- Add a new trusted publisher\n- **Repository owner:** `myorg`\n- **Repository name:** `mylib`\n- **Workflow:** `publish.yml`\n- **Environment:** `nuget` (recommended)\n\n### 2. GitHub Actions workflow\n\nI'll create the workflow file:","toolRequests":[{"toolCallId":"tooluse_KXDXSN4QTm0i6vf7dzwMEK","name":"create","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-a653a29af9b147df8f72b9e5f493895d/.github/workflows/publish.yml","file_text":"name: Publish to NuGet\n\non:\n  push:\n    tags:\n      - 'v*'\n\njobs:\n  publish:\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    environment: nuget\n    permissions:\n      id-token: write # Required for OIDC trusted publishing\n\n    steps:\n      - uses: actions/checkout@v4\n\n      - uses: actions/setup-dotnet@v4\n        with:\n          dotnet-version: '8.0.x'\n\n      - name: Pack\n        run: dotnet pack src/MyLib/MyLib.csproj -c Release -o ./artifacts\n\n      - name: Publish to NuGet\n        run: dotnet nuget push ./artifacts/*.nupkg --source https://api.nuget.org/v3/index.json\n"},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"create a new file at /tmp/sv-a653a29af9b147df8f72b9e5f493895d/.github/workflows/publish.yml."}],"interactionId":"dad05970-cdc6-4fc1-89a8-9ca9e2e51f4a","outputTokens":429,"requestId":"1430:343824:12AD456:14F7A4D:6A027A5B"},"id":"a66505f0-8968-4801-a1a3-d38c91b7f415","timestamp":"2026-05-12T00:54:59.737Z","parentId":"13780891-c34b-461d-832d-183c81d7b233"}
{"type":"tool.execution_start","data":{"toolCallId":"tooluse_KXDXSN4QTm0i6vf7dzwMEK","toolName":"create","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-a653a29af9b147df8f72b9e5f493895d/.github/workflows/publish.yml","file_text":"name: Publish to NuGet\n\non:\n  push:\n    tags:\n      - 'v*'\n\njobs:\n  publish:\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    environment: nuget\n    permissions:\n      id-token: write # Required for OIDC trusted publishing\n\n    steps:\n      - uses: actions/checkout@v4\n\n      - uses: actions/setup-dotnet@v4\n        with:\n          dotnet-version: '8.0.x'\n\n      - name: Pack\n        run: dotnet pack src/MyLib/MyLib.csproj -c Release -o ./artifacts\n\n      - name: Publish to NuGet\n        run: dotnet nuget push ./artifacts/*.nupkg --source https://api.nuget.org/v3/index.json\n"}},"id":"0c150f1b-948c-452b-8741-49176bc7fb64","timestamp":"2026-05-12T00:54:59.738Z","parentId":"a66505f0-8968-4801-a1a3-d38c91b7f415"}
